<div class="about-container-pro">
    <div class="header-section">
        <h2>About This Project</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-section">
        <p>
            <strong class="project-title">BlazorAppWebSearchUsingAI</strong> is a professional web application built with <span class="tech-highlight">Blazor</span> and <span class="tech-highlight">.NET 8</span>. Its primary function is to provide a simple, user-friendly interface for searching people in a database. The application demonstrates <span class="principle-highlight">clean architecture principles</span>, ensuring separation of concerns, maintainability, and scalability.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="architecture-section">
        <h3>Architecture Overview</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Presentation Layer:</strong> <span class="layer-desc">Interactive UI built with Blazor, handling user input and displaying results.</span></li>
            <li><strong>Domain Layer:</strong> <span class="layer-desc">Defines core business entities and repository interfaces for data access.</span></li>
            <li><strong>Application Layer:</strong> <span class="layer-desc">Contains service interfaces for business operations and search logic.</span></li>
            <li><strong>Infrastructure Layer:</strong> <span class="layer-desc">Implements data access using Entity Framework Core and SQL Server.</span></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="features-section">
        <h3>Key Features</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="feature-highlight">Simple search functionality</span> for people records in a database.</li>
            <li>Clean separation of UI, business logic, and data access.</li>
            <li><span class="feature-highlight">Entity Framework Core</span> for robust, scalable data management.</li>
            <li>Configuration-driven messaging for user feedback and validation.</li>
            <li>Easy extensibility for new features and data sources.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

